A Python package with quaternion arithmetics and 3D rotation around an 
arbitrary axis, based on quaternions.

For more information, see docstrings in "quaternion.py" and "rotation.py".
Additionally see unit testing scripts "quaternion_test.py" and
"rotation_test.py".

The package is licenced under the Apache 2.0 license. See LICENSE.txt and
http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0
for more details.

The author of the package is Jernej Kovacic (jkovacic AT gmail DOT com).
